I '''Paul David Hewson''' (mibait 10 Mayo 1960), a mas kilala king kayang talipampan a '''Bono''' ({{IPAc-en|ˈ|b|ɒ|n|oʊ}}), metung yang [[Irish people|Irish]] a magkanta, musikeru, venture capitalist, negosyanti ampong aktibista.<ref>[http://www.oprah.com/spirit/Bono-A-Global-Rock-Star-and-Activist Bono-fire].</ref> Pikabaluan yang dili antimong [[frontman]], manimunang bokalista (''primary vocalist'') ampong talasulat amanu (''lyricist'') ning bandang rock a [[U2]], a makabasi king [[Dublin]]. Mibait ya ampong meragul i Bono king Dublin, Ireland, at megaral ya king [[Mount Temple Comprehensive School]], nung nu la mikit ning kayang ayasawa, i [[Ali Hewson|Alison Stewart]], ampo reng meging kayanib o miembru ning U2 .<ref name=MacphistoNet /><ref name="Bono on Bono" /><ref name=ATU2Clayton /> Alus i Bono ing susulat kareng anggang amanu da reng kanta ning U2, at maralas, gagamit yang temang relihyosu, sosyal, pang-ketawan o pang-ketawan, ampong pampulitika.<ref name=ATU2comBonoBio /><ref name=Stockman /> Anyang mumuna nang banwa ning During U2, sinaup la reng amanu nang Bono king datang nang magrebeldi ampong ispiritwal kareti.<ref name=ATU2comBonoBio /> Anyang melambat ya ing banda, ing meging inspirasyun da reng amanu, deng personal a karanasan nung no nala karake deng aliwang kayanib ning banda.<ref name="Bono on Bono" /><ref name=ATU2comBonoBio />

